        <section id="research">
            <h2>Research Focus</h2>
            <p>Evaporation driven pattern formation is an active area of research in our group. Elucidation of role of particle and substrate charge, orientation of the drop, effect of confinement, and soft-ness of particles on evaporation driven pattern formation are some areas where we have made notable contributions.</p>
